Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;<br />
The kite flies<br />
Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;<br />
The kite flies</p>
<p>Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;<br />
The kite flies<br />
Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;</p>
<p>Stuck by a thread that never unrolls itself<br />
I have a kite made of paper and glue<br />
When I fly it, it seems to have a spring<br />
Always asking to go up</p>
<p>Kite, you fly and forget my age<br />
Pull by the thread of my own will<br />
Try to find the road to the truth<br />
And I will try to follow you</p>
<p>Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;<br />
The kite flies<br />
Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;<br />
The kite flies</p>
<p>Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;<br />
The kite flies<br />
Dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li, dai li dou&#8230;</p>
<p>Tell me all the things you see, my friend<br />
I&#8217;m on Earth, dreaming of being with you<br />
Even if I&#8217;m in the middle of danger<br />
I&#8217;ll resist, only to listen to you</p>
<p>Each morning I&#8217;ll be like a child<br />
Playing in the fields, flying in hope<br />
I dived into the star which no one reaches<br />
But I&#8217;ll make it<br />
But I&#8217;ll make it, dai li dou&#8230;</p>
